 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the tower house##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the craftsman house##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the cottage house##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person eating radish##1

